                    <p>Etihad Airways is one of the prestigious airlines in the United Arab Emirates. After Emirates, it is the second-largest airline in UAE. Etihad Airways operates more than 1,000 flights per week to over 120 passenger and cargo destinations in the Middle East, Africa, Europe, Asia, Australia, and North America, with a fleet of 102 aircraft. In 2014, the airline introduced new cabins in its various aircraft. </p>
